column1: Sugar said "Um no thanks, thats sweet of you to ask though!"
Stephenie said "I really cant say for sure if I trust you"
Cercie said "Good things come to those who wait"
Tom said "Listen lets not focus on the game, we got work to do"
James said " Cmon, why are you always talking about the game"
J.T. said "You know Im not sure what I am going to do"
Amanda said "Thats not going to work with me right now
Candice said "Can I get back to you in a few days?"
Rupert said "Listen we can trust each other, theres no need for alliances
Colby said "Aw shucks, well Im not much for stragy"
Sugar said "Thats so sweet of you to think of me!"
Stephenie said "I trust you, you trust me"
Cercie said "You have patience I want to work with you"
Tom said "Youre one of the hardest workers here, we can work together"
James said "Hell yeah, lets take this baby to the final three"
J.T. said "I won my last game with a solid alliance, lets do it again"
Amanda said "Finally someone with some sense in this game"
Candice said "We can work together!"
Rupert said "There are villians among us, we must work together"
Colby said "Well partner, I guess we outta sick together"
Sugar said "Wow what a nasty thing to say"
Stephenie said "You think your funny?"
Cercie said "Well I dont like your attitude"
Tom said "Now thats just plain disrespectful"
James said "How about I knock your teeth out?"
J.T. said "We dont say things like that where I come from"
Amanda said "Youre such a jerk"
Candice said "I cannot even deal with you right now"
Rupert said "Talk to me like that and I will snap your puny neck"
Colby said "I know you didnt mean it but that was rude"
Sugar said "Youre the sweetest"
Stephenie said "The more we talk the more I like you"
Cercie said "Youre lucky youre so funny"
Tom said "Now thats a worker"
James said "Give me a hug"
J.T. said "Thats the nicest thing anyone has ever said to me"
Amanda says "Youre a good friend"
Candice said "Thanks for being there"
Rupert said "Youre like the child I never had"
Colby said "Now thats a real handshake right there, one you can trust"
Sugar said "We cannot talk anymore"
Stephenie said "You are going home NEXT!"
Cercie said "Hmm"
Tom said "Youre a lazy bum"
James said "You next! Ya hear me you next!"
J.T. said "That is not kind of you I will remember that"
Amanda said "What did I EVER DO TO YOU"
Candice said "Fuck you"
Rupert said "You are a snake in the grass and I will not tolerate a snake"
Colby said "Wish you had not have said that"
Sugar said "We should talk more"
Stephenie said "I did not know you liked that thing too"
Cercie said "Could you get me some water"
Tom said "Keep working hard like you are"
James said "Dude I am trying to sleep"
J.T. said "I like your attitude"
Amanda said "Are you hitting on me"
Candice said "I have to go for a walk"
Rupert said "Let us go fishing sometime"
Colby said "Let get to work"
Yasmin said "Lets do this!"
Russell said "God is on our side"
Erik said "One of us is  gonna win"
Kelly said "We will make a great team"
John said "You are the best"
Dave said "We are brothers now"
Monica said "I guess that will work"
Shambo "OH YEAHHH"
Brett said "I do not have anything to say"
Laura said "We can dominate this game"
Yasmin said "I dont know about that"
Russell said "W're all a team no need for that"
Erik said "That wont work for me right now"
Kelly said "Yeah I do not want to do that right now
John said "Chill with this game talk"
Dave said "What do you even mean"
Monica said "Careful playing that hard"
Shambo said "WHAT?"
Brett said "I got nothing"
Laura said "Not now"
Yasmin said "You think you can talk to me like that"
Russell said "You are the work of the devil"
Erik said "I cant believe you"
Kelly said "That was super uncalled for"
John said "Im gunning for you now"
Dave said "I wont take this anymore"
Monica said "That was your last straw"
Shambo said "Youre an unlawful citizen"
Brett said "I do not know what to say to that"
Laura said "Wow screw you"
Yasmin "You have no idea how much that means to me"
Russell said "God with ya brother"
Erik said" Youre gonna make me cry"
Kelly said "You make this game easier "
John said "Hey thanks for always working so hard"
Dave said "Youre a sweetheat"
Monica said "Youre such a charmer"
Shambo said "OH I LIKE YOU"
Brett said "I am speechless"
Laura said "I could kiss you"
Yasmin said "I am a little busy to talk"
Russle said "Theres work to do"
Erik said "Not now"
Kelly said "Listen I gotta sleep"
John said "Please I need to relax right now"
Dave said "I cannot talk right now"
Monica said "Can we eat before we talk"
Shambo said "WHAT WAS THAT"
Brett said "I do not know what to say "
Laura said "We can talk after the challenge"
Yasmin said "Thats not a nice thing to say"
Russell said "You need Jesus"
Erik said "That was scummy"
Kelly said "Do you have manners"
John said "Fuck you"
Dave said "What is that supposed to mean"
Monica said "Youre a coward"
Shamboo "SAY THAT TO MY FACE"
Brett said "I cant even speak"
Laura said "That was uncalled for"
